// =====================================================================================
// Copilot Studio – ODSP-in-Agentic-Work Scorecard (Level 201)
// VALIDATED against CAP Analytics on 2026-07-16 (pulled live from all 19 FDA Island
// regional clusters). Implements the taxonomy Ambal proposed:
//   Prod / Non-Prod  x  C1 / C2 / Total  x  {Active Users, Active Tenants,
//   Active Agents, Tasks, Tool Calls}  for Last-wk vs This-wk (rolling 7d).
// Source logic from the "ODSP + Copilot Studio Data Sync" working session
// (Sandeep Yerra, 2026-07-16), reconciled with the real TraceEvents schema.
//
// CONFIRMED schema (CAP Analytics . TraceEvents):
//   env_time                         timestamp
//   applicationName                  Dracarys apps = "fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticRuntime",
//                                                    "fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticLoopApp"
//   eventName                        KnowledgeSourceLatency  -> knowledge queries / activity proxy
//                                    AgenticLoopToolCallLatency -> tool calls
//                                    AgenticLoopTurnLatency     -> turns / conversations
//                                    AgenticLoopLLMCallLatency  -> LLM calls
//   principalObjectId                user id
//   customDimensions (JSON)          .TenantId .CdsBotId (agent) .ConversationId
//                                    .IsDesignMode ("True"/"False") -> Non-Prod / Prod
//                                    .BotSchemaName .IsAITeammate .ChannelId .EnvironmentId
//   message (JSON)                   .Success
//
// Clusters (fan-out): fdislandsus.centralus (Central US) + 18 regional peers. The full
// 19-way union over 14–30d TIMES OUT; run PER-CLUSTER and SUM distinct counts client-side
// ("sum of per-region distincts ~= global"), which the dashboard already does.
//
// OPEN ITEMS (confirm with Sandeep):
//   * C1 vs C2 (builder/enterprise vs user-created) has NO field in TraceEvents
//     customDimensions -> needs an agent-classification lookup / registry.
//   * Non-Prod: meeting scope = eval + test + auto-provisioned + first-person/system.
//     IsDesignMode==True is a first-cut proxy (design-mode / authoring & test).
//   * Active Users/Tenants/Agents are ALL gated on AgenticLoopTurnLatency (turn-active),
//     a single consistent basis. Active Agents on this basis (This-wk 52.4K per-region /
//     52.1K global) reconciles with Sandeep's cited ~48.5K; the earlier
//     KnowledgeSourceLatency basis undercounted Agents to ~26K. Users/Tenants likewise
//     moved to turn basis (Users 27K->49K, Tenants 10K->11.5K global, This-wk).
//     NOTE: all-up Total is an INDEPENDENT distinct (not Prod+NonProd), because an
//     entity can be active in both design and non-design mode.
// =====================================================================================

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// PER-CLUSTER metric query. Run once per island; sum results in the driver. Substitute
// <ISLAND> with each of:
//   fdislandsae.uaenorth, fdislandsas.southeastasia, fdislandsau.australiaeast,
//   fdislandsbr.brazilsouth, fdislandsca.canadacentral, fdislandsch.switzerlandnorth,
//   fdislandsde.germanywestcentral, fdislandseu.westeurope, fdislandsfr.francecentral,
//   fdislandsin.centralindia, fdislandsjp.japaneast, fdislandskr.koreasouth,
//   fdislandsno.norwayeast, fdislandsse.swedencentral, fdislandsit.italynorth,
//   fdislandssg.southeastasia, fdislandsuk.uksouth, fdislandsza.southafricanorth,
//   fdislandsus.centralus
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cluster('<ISLAND>.kusto.windows.net').database('CAPAnalytics').TraceEvents
| where env_time > ago(14d)
| where applicationName in ("fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticRuntime", "fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticLoopApp")
| where eventName in ('KnowledgeSourceLatency','AgenticLoopToolCallLatency','AgenticLoopTurnLatency')
| extend wk  = iff(env_time > ago(7d), 'This', 'Last')
| extend meta = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend UserId   = tostring(principalObjectId),
         TenantId = tostring(meta.TenantId),
         AgentId  = tostring(meta.CdsBotId),
         ConvId   = tostring(meta.ConversationId),
         Env      = iff(tostring(meta.IsDesignMode) == 'True', 'NonProd', 'Prod')
| summarize
    ActiveUsers   = dcountif(UserId,   eventName == 'AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(UserId)),   // turn-active (consistent basis)
    ActiveTenants = dcountif(TenantId, eventName == 'AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(TenantId)),
    ActiveAgents  = dcountif(AgentId,  eventName == 'AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(AgentId)),  // agents that ran >=1 task; reconciles with Sandeep ~48.5K
    Tasks         = dcountif(ConvId,   eventName == 'AgenticLoopTurnLatency'  and isnotempty(ConvId)),
    ToolCalls     = countif(eventName == 'AgenticLoopToolCallLatency')
  by wk, Env
// Driver: sum each metric across all islands, by (wk, Env). NOTE: for distinct metrics
// (Users/Tenants/Agents), the all-up Total is an INDEPENDENT distinct, NOT Prod+NonProd
// (an entity can appear in both modes). Per-region sum ~= true global distinct: verified
// within <1% for Users & Agents (Tenants ~5% higher) against the single-union dcount below.

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// GLOBAL DISTINCT (headline totals) – single lean union across all 19 clusters. This
// COMPLETES (~minutes) because it filters to turn events only and projects just the ids.
// (Union list abbreviated; include all 19 cluster('<ISLAND>.kusto.windows.net') refs.)
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// union
//   cluster('fdislandsus.centralus.kusto.windows.net').database('CAPAnalytics').TraceEvents,
//   cluster('fdislandseu.westeurope.kusto.windows.net').database('CAPAnalytics').TraceEvents,
//   ... (all 19 islands) ...
// | where env_time > ago(14d)
// | where applicationName in ("fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticRuntime", "fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticLoopApp")
// | where eventName == 'AgenticLoopTurnLatency'
// | extend meta = parse_json(customDimensions)
// | project UserId = tostring(principalObjectId), TenantId = tostring(meta.TenantId),
//           AgentId = tostring(meta.CdsBotId), last7 = env_time > ago(7d)
// | summarize
//     U_This = dcountif(UserId,   last7 and isnotempty(UserId)),   U_Last = dcountif(UserId,   not(last7) and isnotempty(UserId)),
//     T_This = dcountif(TenantId, last7 and isnotempty(TenantId)), T_Last = dcountif(TenantId, not(last7) and isnotempty(TenantId)),
//     A_This = dcountif(AgentId,  last7 and isnotempty(AgentId)),  A_Last = dcountif(AgentId,  not(last7) and isnotempty(AgentId))

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// MAINLINE view: identical, but replace the applicationName filter with everything NOT
// in the Dracarys apps:
//   | where applicationName !in ("fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticRuntime", "fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticLoopApp")
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// 301 – ODSP-in-Copilot-Studio footprint: add an ODSP connector filter. ODSP tools =
// SharePoint / OneDrive connectors (e.g. "Get File Item", "Get File Content"). Confirm
// the connector/tool field + IDs from the ToolCall event's customDimensions.
//   | where <toolCategory/connector field> has_any ("SharePoint","OneDrive", ...)   <<CONFIRM>>
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// LIVE RESULT (pulled 2026-07-16, all-up Dracarys, TURN-BASED, summed per-region).
// Windows are Sun-Sat (rolling two weeks): Last = Jun 28-Jul 4, This = Jul 5-11 (2026).
// To reproduce, replace `ago(14d)` with explicit bounds:
//   | where env_time >= datetime(2026-06-28) and env_time < datetime(2026-07-12)
//   | extend wk = iff(env_time >= datetime(2026-07-05),'This','Last')
// Total-column caveat: for Users/Tenants/Agents the true all-up is an independent global
// distinct (see GLOBAL section), not Prod+NonProd.
//   Last wk (Jun 28-Jul 4)  Prod / NonProd  (per-region sum)
//     Active Users     26,441 /  3,903
//     Active Tenants    7,764 /  1,753
//     Active Agents    34,561 /  6,789
//     Tasks           430,998 / 51,015
//     Tool Calls    1,395,706 /120,710
//   This wk (Jul 5-11)      Prod / NonProd  (per-region sum)
//     Active Users     32,361 / 12,355
//     Active Tenants    8,325 /  5,635
//     Active Agents    33,985 / 20,735
//     Tasks           609,229 /105,626
//     Tool Calls    3,258,237 /371,151
//
// TRUE GLOBAL DISTINCT (single union across all 19 clusters, turn basis) -- headline totals:
//                     Last wk (Jun28-Jul4) / This wk (Jul5-11)
//     Active Users    29,051 / 40,334
//     Active Tenants   7,921 /  9,881
//     Active Agents   39,532 / 48,592   (~= the cited ~48.5K)
//   All-up Tasks (additive) 482,013 / 714,855 ; Tool Calls 1,516,416 / 3,629,388.
// The lean single-union dcount (turn events only, project 3 ids) DOES complete (~minutes);
// prefer it for headline totals. Prod/NonProd split still comes from the per-region pull.
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

// =====================================================================================
// ALL-UP PLATFORM C1 / C2 (curated) -- NEW source, unblocks the C1/C2 split that
// TraceEvents cannot provide. Cluster mspva01.westus2, DB csinternaltelemetry.
// This is a DISTINCT, BROADER scope than the Dracarys agentic-loop tables above; do NOT
// compare row-for-row. C1 = builder/enterprise (Copilot Agents C1, licensed BizChat
// context). C2 = end-user self-created declarative/custom agents. TestCanvas: True =
// test canvas (Non-Prod), False = published/live (Prod). "Weekly*" columns = trailing-7d
// WAU. Pulled live 2026-07-16 (data snapshots dated per query below).
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

// --- C1 users (fresh, snapshot 2026-07-15) ---
CAC1UsersByTenantId
| where Timestamp == toscalar(CAC1UsersByTenantId | summarize max(Timestamp))
| summarize C1_Users_WAU = sum(WAU), C1_Users_MAU = sum(MAU), C1_Tenants = dcount(TenantId)
// -> C1_Users_WAU 244,317 ; C1_Tenants 122,686

// --- C1 tenants (pre-aggregated, fresh) ---
CAC1Tenants
| where Timestamp == toscalar(CAC1Tenants | summarize max(Timestamp))
| project WAT, DAT, MAT
// -> WAT 40,571

// --- C2 users/tenants (fresh, snapshot 2026-07-15) ---
AllActiveC2UsersByTenantId
| where Date == toscalar(AllActiveC2UsersByTenantId | summarize max(Date))
| summarize C2_Users_WAU = sum(WeeklyUserCount), C2_AuthUsers_WAU = sum(WeeklyAuthenticatedUserCount), C2_Tenants = dcount(TenantId)
// -> C2_Users_WAU 8,363,628 (auth 1,282,955) ; C2_Tenants 121,557

// --- C2 custom agents/users x Prod/Non-Prod (TestCanvas), fresh ---
ActiveCustomAgentsAndC2UsersByTenantId
| where Timestamp == toscalar(ActiveCustomAgentsAndC2UsersByTenantId | summarize max(Timestamp))
| summarize Agents = sum(WeeklyActiveAgentCount), Users = sum(WeeklyUserCount),
            Interactions = sum(WeeklyInteractionsCount), Tenants = dcount(TenantId) by TestCanvas
| order by TestCanvas
// -> False(Prod): Agents 132,757 / Users 7,582,835 / Interactions 48.37M / Tenants 39,403
//    True (NonProd): Agents 187,640 / Users   139,535 / Interactions  2.64M / Tenants 61,923
//    AUTHORITATIVE CS active-agents (prod, custom) = 132,757 (fresh 2026-07-15).

// --- Autonomous agents (prod), fresh -- matches cited 39,283 (0.1%) ---
ActiveAutonomousAgentsByTenantId
| where Timestamp == toscalar(ActiveAutonomousAgentsByTenantId | summarize max(Timestamp))
| summarize Agents = sum(WeeklyActiveAgentCount), Tenants = dcount(TenantId) by TestCanvas
// -> False: Agents 39,233 ; Tenants 13,167

// --- Tool calls + ODSP-SharePoint split by IsB2E  (STALE snapshot 2025-09-09; reference only) ---
AgentsTrafficAggregatedBreakdown
| where Timestamp == toscalar(AgentsTrafficAggregatedBreakdown | summarize max(Timestamp))
| summarize WeeklyAllTools = sum(WeeklyAllTools), WeeklyAllActions = sum(WeeklyAllActions),
            WeeklyAllKnowledge = sum(WeeklyAllKnowledge),
            WeeklySPKnowledge = sum(WeeklySharepointKnowledgeSearches),
            WeeklyGraphSearches = sum(WeeklyGraphSearches),
            ActiveBots = dcount(BotId), Tenants = dcount(TenantId) by IsB2E
| order by IsB2E
// -> IsB2E true (enterprise): AllTools 1,889,597 / SP searches 148,942 / bots 100,773
//    IsB2E false (consumer):  AllTools 23,700,408 / SP searches 363,563 / bots 673,321
//    CAVEAT: last refreshed 2025-09-09 -- STALE (~10mo). Shown for reference only.

// --- (STALE) DeclarativeAgentsActiveC2ByTenantId_Temp -- source of the cited 249,381 ---
DeclarativeAgentsActiveC2ByTenantId_Temp
| where Date == toscalar(DeclarativeAgentsActiveC2ByTenantId_Temp | summarize max(Date))
| summarize C2_ActiveAgents_WAU = sum(WeeklyActiveAgents), C2_Users_WAU = sum(WAU), C2_Tenants = dcount(TenantId)
// -> WeeklyActiveAgents 248,023 (~= cited 249,381) BUT last refreshed 2025-11-01 -- STALE.
//    Superseded by the fresh ActiveCustomAgentsAndC2UsersByTenantId prod count 132,757.
// =====================================================================================

// =====================================================================================
// ODSP IN COPILOT STUDIO -- 301 FOOTPRINT + % of CS, 401 PERFORMANCE, per-connector
// Scope: Dracarys agentic-loop (CAPAnalytics TraceEvents), 19 FDA-Island regional
// clusters, per-region distinct counts summed client-side (~ global). Sun-Sat windows:
//   Last = Jun 28-Jul 4 (2026-06-28 .. <2026-07-05) ; This = Jul 5-11 (.. <2026-07-12).
// ODSP tool = AgenticLoopToolCallLatency whose connector (segment after /apim/) is one
// of {sharepointonline, onedriveforbusiness, workiqsharepoint, workiqonedrive,
// sharepointembedded} OR a direct *.sharepoint.com / onedrive URL (no apim connector).
// Success = customDimensions.Success (fallback message.Success); latency =
// customDimensions.TotalMilliseconds. Pulled live 2026-07-16 (per-cluster fan-out).
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// 301 footprint + %-of-CS + 401 turn-success (single pass; run per regional cluster, sum)
TraceEvents
| where env_time >= datetime(2026-06-28) and env_time < datetime(2026-07-12)
| where applicationName in ("fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticRuntime","fabric:/CopilotStudio.AgenticLoopApp")
| where eventName in ('AgenticLoopToolCallLatency','AgenticLoopTurnLatency')
| extend wk = iff(env_time >= datetime(2026-07-05),'This','Last')
| extend meta = parse_json(customDimensions), msg = parse_json(message)
| extend UserId=tostring(principalObjectId), TenantId=tostring(meta.TenantId),
         ConvId=tostring(meta.ConversationId), Url=tostring(meta.SanitizedUrl),
         Ms=todouble(meta.TotalMilliseconds)
| extend Success = iff(isnotempty(tostring(meta.Success)), tostring(meta.Success), tostring(msg.Success))
| extend Conn = tolower(extract(@"/apim/([^/]+)/", 1, Url))
| extend IsODSP = (eventName=='AgenticLoopToolCallLatency') and (
        Conn in ("sharepointonline","onedriveforbusiness","workiqsharepoint","workiqonedrive","sharepointembedded")
        or (isempty(Conn) and Url matches regex @"(?i)(\.sharepoint\.com|onedrive)") )
| summarize
    ODSP_Users=dcountif(UserId, IsODSP and isnotempty(UserId)),
    ODSP_Tenants=dcountif(TenantId, IsODSP and isnotempty(TenantId)),
    ODSP_Tasks=dcountif(ConvId, IsODSP and isnotempty(ConvId)),
    ODSP_ToolCalls=countif(IsODSP),
    ODSP_ToolSucc=countif(IsODSP and Success=='True'),
    ODSP_MsSum=sumif(Ms, IsODSP and isnotnull(Ms)), ODSP_MsCnt=countif(IsODSP and isnotnull(Ms)),
    CS_Users=dcountif(UserId, eventName=='AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(UserId)),
    CS_Tenants=dcountif(TenantId, eventName=='AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(TenantId)),
    CS_Tasks=dcountif(ConvId, eventName=='AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and isnotempty(ConvId)),
    CS_ToolCalls=countif(eventName=='AgenticLoopToolCallLatency'),
    CS_TurnTotal=countif(eventName=='AgenticLoopTurnLatency'),
    CS_TurnSucc=countif(eventName=='AgenticLoopTurnLatency' and Success=='True')
  by wk
// -- per-connector (401 tool health): swap the summarize for:
//   | extend Conn2 = case(Conn in (...ODSP set...), Conn,
//        isempty(Conn) and Url matches regex @"(?i)\.sharepoint\.com","sharepoint_direct",
//        isempty(Conn) and Url matches regex @"(?i)onedrive","onedrive_direct","other")
//   | where Conn2 != "other"
//   | summarize Calls=count(), Succ=countif(Success=='True'),
//               MsSum=sumif(Ms,isnotnull(Ms)), MsCnt=countif(isnotnull(Ms)) by wk, Conn2
// =====================================================================================
// LIVE RESULT (pulled 2026-07-16, Sun-Sat; Last=Jun28-Jul4, This=Jul5-11):
// 301 FOOTPRINT (Total):  Users 1,826 -> 6,564 | Tenants 752 -> 2,579 |
//                         Tasks 16,014 -> 53,473 | Tool calls 45,327 -> 213,980
//   C1/C2 NOT derivable at this scope (no builder-vs-user classifier in TraceEvents).
// 301 % of CS:  Users 6.3% -> 16.2% | Tenants 8.9% -> 24.6% |
//               Tasks 3.3% -> 7.5%  | Tool calls 3.0% -> 5.9%
//   CS all-up denominators: Users 28,981->40,397 | Tenants 8,419->10,485 |
//                           Tasks 481,950->714,056 | ToolCalls 1,516,416->3,629,388
// 401 PERFORMANCE:  Tool success 92.7% -> 71.6% (v 21.1pp) |
//                   Turn success 97.6% -> 98.3% (^ 0.7pp) | Avg latency 1,179ms -> 606ms
//   Driver of tool-success drop = SharePoint Online (46.8% of ODSP calls) -> 52.9%.
// PER-CONNECTOR (Last succ% -> This succ% ; This share%):
//   SharePoint Online    77.3 -> 52.9 ; 46.8%   OneDrive (direct)  81.3 -> 61.3 ; 11.3%
//   SharePoint (direct)  94.6 -> 94.7 ; 36.5%   WorkIQ SharePoint  99.5 -> 99.5 ;  4.1%
//   WorkIQ OneDrive      99.2 -> 99.8 ;  1.0%   OneDrive for Bus.  85.5 -> 86.1 ;  0.3%
//   Total ODSP calls: 45,327 -> 213,980.
// =====================================================================================
